<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's just sold her directorial feature debut Bruised to Netflix in a rumored eight figure deal.</p>

<p>And Halle Berry has also gone pubic with a new romance, confirming she's in a relationship with singer Van Hunt.</p>

<p>On Sunday, the actress, 54, shared a selfie to Instagram in which she's seen with her 50-year-old beau.</p>

<p>'You’ve got to COORDINATE': Berry, 54, shared a selfie to Instagram on Sunday in which she's seen with her new beau Van Hunt, 50, wearing matching black cloth face masks </p>

<p>The photo and caption served as an encouragement to her social media followers to abide by the wearing mask rule during the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic.</p>

<p>Both Berry and Hunt are seen in the selfie wearing matching black cloth face masks and in the caption, the Monster's Ball Oscar winner wrote: 'You’ve got to COORDINATE. #MasksSaveLives.'</p>

<p>The post comes a week after Berry confirmed her new romance by posting to Instagram a snap in which she's shown planting a kiss on the musician's cheek.</p>

<p>Couple alert: The post comes a week after Berry confirmed her new romance by posting to Instagram a snap in which she's shown planting a kiss on the musician's cheek</p>

<p>Hunt, who hails from Dayton, Ohio, has toured with Kanye West, Mary J. Blige, Coldplay, Dave Matthews Band, Afghan Wigs and The Roots.</p>

<p>He won a Grammy back in 2007 for his work on a cover of the Sly &amp; the Family Stone song Family Affair.</p>

<p>Berry's film Bruised premiered at the Toronto International Film Festival earlier this month.</p>

<p>The drama, which she also stars in, is set in the world of mixed martial arts.</p>

<p>The former Die Another Day Bond girl plays a former MMA fighter who has lost custody of her son and embarks on a mission to regain both her child and her career. </p>

<p>In the money: Earlier this month, it was reported that Berry's directorial debut, gritty drama Bruised, in which she also stars, had been sold to Netflix for a rumored eight-figure sum </p>

<p>She was last seen on the big screen in last year's John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum opposite Keanu Reeves. </p>

<p>Berry has been married three times and divorced three times.</p>

<p>She has two children, daughter Nahla, 12, with ex-boyfriend Gabriel Aubry, and son Mateo, six, with third husband Olivier Martinez.</p>

